title: El Burro Spanish Restaurant
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Mediterranean, Beer/Wine, Spanish, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Spanish restaurant with a few vegan choices which include 2 appetizers, 1 shared plate, 4 side dishes, paella and 1 dessert. Dishes that are vegan or can be: aceitunas, chips de maiz, encuritidos fritos (omit aioli), champinones (omit butter), remolacha beet salad, (omit cheese), corn cob, (omit mayo, cheese), arroz saffron rice, bravas (omit aioli), and vegetal paella.
